    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in SEEING RED, a single-player, first-person survival horror experience that pulls you into a chilling narrative filled with suspense and mystery. You step into the shoes of Benjamin, an ex-military private detective whose troubled past comes back to haunt him when he returns to his forgotten childhood town.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SEEING RED</strong> is a full-featured first-person survival horror game that offers an intense and immersive experience. This product includes:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Full Story Campaign</strong> – A gripping, atmospheric narrative following your search for your missing sister, uncovering dark secrets along the way. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>First-Person Combat</strong> – Use firearms and melee weapons to fight off relentless monsters, but beware—ammo and stamina are limited.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stealth &amp; Evasion</strong> – Hide, run, or find alternative ways to survive against creatures hunting you.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Investigation &amp; Exploration</strong> – Search for clues, interact with NPCs, and uncover the town’s dark secrets through dialogue and environmental storytelling.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Decision-Making</strong> – Your choices affect how the story unfolds, leading to different outcomes and interactions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Puzzles &amp; Lore Discovery</strong> – Solve cryptic puzzles, piece together hidden lore, and unveil the truth behind the horrors that surround you.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive Horror Experience</strong> – Photorealistic visuals, dynamic sound design, and psychological horror elements that heighten tension and fear.</p></li></ul><p class=\